    "q": "<span class=\"q-prefix\">Q. 20년 3회</span><div class=\"question-box\"><p data-ke-size=\"size16\" id=\"SE-a37175b1-db68-4fee-bf4d-9f0d4dc186c5\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">17번 출력 결과</span></p><pre class=\"java\" data-ke-language=\"java\" data-ke-type=\"codeblock\" id=\"code_1671097078833\"><code>public class Main {\n\tpublic static void main(String[] args){\n    int i=0, sum=0;\n    while (i&lt;10){\n    \ti++;\n        if(i%2 ==1)\n        \tcontinue;\n        sum += i;\n     }\n     System.out.println(sum);\n   }\n}</code></pre></div>정답: [[\\n30]]",
