    "q": "<span class=\"q-prefix\">Q. 23년 2회</span><div class=\"question-box\"><p data-ke-size=\"size16\">14번 출력결과</p><pre class=\"java\" data-ke-language=\"java\" data-ke-type=\"codeblock\" id=\"code_1690712749830\"><code>public class Main {\npublic static void main(String[] args) {\n\t  String str1 = \"Programming\"; \n      String str2 = \"Programming\";\n      String str3 = new String(\"Programming\");\n      \n      System.out.println(str1==str2);\n      System.out.println(str1==str3);\n      System.out.println(str1.equals(str3));\n      System.out.print(str2.equals(str3));\n}\n}</code></pre></div>정답: [[\\ntrue\\nfalse\\ntrue\\ntrue]]",
