    "q": "<span class=\"q-prefix\">Q. 23년 3회</span><div class=\"question-box\"><p data-ke-size=\"size16\">14번 출력결과(20년 4회 19번과 문제 동일)</p><pre class=\"java\" data-ke-language=\"java\" data-ke-type=\"codeblock\" id=\"code_1697771463392\"><code>class Parent {\n\tint compute(int num) {\n\t\tif(num &lt;= 1)\n\t\t\treturn num;\n\t\treturn compute(num-1) + compute(num-2);\n\t}\n}\nclass Child extends Parent {\n\tint compute(int num) {\n\t\tif(num &lt;= 1)\n\t\t\treturn num;\n\t\treturn compute(num-1) + compute(num-3);\n\t}\n}\npublic class Main {\n\tpublic static void main(String args[]) {\n\t\tParent obj = new Child();\n\t\tSystem.out.print(obj.compute(7));\n\t}\n}</code></pre></div>정답: [[\\n2]]",
